üåë
My anxiety has been manageable but at times I still get really overwhelmed and as a result, very irritable. This isn‚Äôt great for everyone around me and I‚Äôve been trying my best to calm down but having a therapist made that so much more easier. As I told her once ‚Äúshe helps me untangle my brain‚Äù ü§∑üèΩ‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è 
üåë
